  "strategy": [
    "Alternate between short forward moves and scanning rotations to maximize marker detection.",
    "Use commit states to enforce persistence of actions and prevent oscillations.",
    "Upon marker detection, immediately pursue the marker with move_to_marker until close.",
    "When close to the marker, stop to ensure safe task completion.",
    "After obstacle recovery or forward commit, insert scan states to avoid long straight runs.",
    "Handle all uncontrollable events in every state for robustness.",
    "Never allow move_forward after obstacle_front without a recovery/scan.",
    "Avoid offering both rotation directions in any state to prevent oscillations.",
    "Return to exploration (scan) only if the marker is lost.",
    "Prioritize marker pursuit over exploration when marker is seen."
